<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center mt-10 lg:mt-20" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('HomeTop.png') %>');">
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col mb-6 lg:mb-16 lg:flex-row mb-1">
      <h1 class="hidden lg:block text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-16 lg:visible mb-10 ml-8 pr-4 pt-2">Welcome To</h1>
      <h1 class="text-7xl font-extrabold text-black mb-10 lg:ml-8 pr-4 text-8xl">Face</h1>
      <h1 class="text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-10 text-8xl">World</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:flex-row">
      <% if logged_in? === false %>
        <%= button_to 'ゲスト', guest_login_path, method: :post, class: 'bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 shadow-xl shadow-red-700/50 text-white py-3 px-7 rounded-full font-semibold text-2xl   ' %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to 'マイヒストリー', user_path(current_user.id), class: 'bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 shadow-xl shadow-red-700/50 text-white py-3 px-6 pt-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-xl ' %>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to '撮影', capture_path, class: 'bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 shadow-xl shadow-blue-700/50 text-white py-3 px-10 lg:mx-1 rounded-full font-semibold text-2xl' %>
      <%= link_to '投稿一覧', posts_path, class: 'bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 shadow-xl shadow-green-700/50 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-full font-semibold text-2xl' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-200 py-20">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-10 lg:mx-72 pt-1 lg:pt-6 " >
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 pt-3">【 撮影方法 】</h1>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "CameraPage.png", class:"w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 h-1/2"%>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-sm lg:text-xl mb-4 pt-3 px-3 lg:px-0">画面中央に顔を合わせて「撮影」ボタンを押してください。<br>撮影が完了すると「分析」ボタンが表示されます。<br>再撮影も可能です。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white mt-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-10 lg:mx-72 pt-1 lg:pt-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 pt-3">【 分析画面 】</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row item-center justify-center mx-3">
      <%= image_tag "DetectPage(1).png", class:"w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 h-1/2"%>
      <%= image_tag "DetectPage(2).png", class:"w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 h-1/2"%>
    </div>
    <div class="flex  items-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-sm lg:text-xl mb-4 pt-3 px-3 lg:px-0">ぼかしボタンを押すとプレビュー画像がぼかされます。<br>感情パラメーターと顔の情報が表示されます。<br>ログイン時は「投稿」ボタンを押して投稿できます。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white mt-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-10 lg:mx-72 pt-1 lg:pt-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 pt-3">【 投稿一覧 】</h1>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "PostindexPage.png", class:"w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 h-1/2"%>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-sm lg:text-xl mb-4 pt-3 px-3 lg:px-0">各投稿をクリックすると、投稿詳細画面に遷移します。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white mt-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-10 lg:mx-72 pt-1 lg:pt-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 pt-3">【 投稿詳細 】</h1>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "PostshowPage.png", class:"w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 h-1/2"%>
    <div class="flexitems-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-sm lg:text-xl mb-4 pt-3 px-3 lg:px-0">各投稿ではコメント投稿やいいねができます。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-white mt-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg mx-10 lg:mx-72 pt-1 lg:pt-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-2 pt-3">【 マイヒストリー 】</h1>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag "UsershowPage.png", class:"w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 h-1/2"%>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-sm lg:text-xl mb-4 pt-3 px-3 lg:px-0">自分の投稿一覧といいねした投稿一覧が確認できます。<br>フォローとフォロワーの一覧が確認できます。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="returnTop"></div>